query:
SELECT p.*, pc.name as category_name, rh.detected_at, rh.was_notified
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.category_id = pc.id
LEFT JOIN restock_history rh ON p.id = rh.product_id
WHERE p.last_seen_at > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)
ORDER BY rh.detected_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
